t:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj7c4o2et2p\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">③ 草图/截图复刻 (Image-to-Diagram)</span></span></ms-cmark-node></h4>\n  <h4 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj7c711h1ud4\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mj7c711p6as\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">你在白板上随手画的草图，或者看到别人文档里的一张好图，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">直接截图上传给它</span>，AI 能分析图片内容，把它重绘成可编辑的 Draw.io 矢量图。</span></ms-cmark-node></h4>\n  <h4 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj7c4o2e1h5p\">再也不用对着别人的图一点点照猫画虎了。</span></ms-cmark-node></h4>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:16px;margin-right:8px;\"></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <ms-cmark-node data-mpa-action-id=\"mj7c79gppr4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj7c79gh3tw\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">④ 基于&nbsp;</span></span><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj7c79gh16z3\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;MS-CMARK-NODE&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Draw.io</span></span></ms-cmark-node>\n   </ms-cmark-node>\n  </h4>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj7c4o2e129t\">因为它是基于 Draw.io 的，内置了 AWS、GCP、Azure 等主流云厂商的图标库。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj7c4o2euo1\">你让它画云架构图时，它会自动使用官方图标，而不是随便给你弄个方块写上名字，专业度直接拉满。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj7c4o2e1jif\">而且原本 Draw.io 的相关管理能力都具备，整体功能挺完备的。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:16px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100046058\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0818363273453093\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1002\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f5ed89d4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePw3ZeGRruyXgImQCaYo8jLuveP7E5qFXib5Tic7koA4RDH4GFJciaaoTIoYyaWiayu2iaqWCQ5sdu4ZcbXVKZUTEGQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <mpcpc class=\"js_c